# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:11
translate portuguese jamiephone1_8f448c11:

    # "I feel my phone buzzing and pull it out of my pocket."
    "Sinto o meu telemóvel a vibrar e tiro-o do bolso."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:13
translate portuguese jamiephone1_9d0e5e2b:

    # "It's Jamie. I answer and lie down on the bed to talk."
    "É o Jamie. Atendo e deito-me na cama para falar."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:18
translate portuguese jamiephone1_14dc4818:

    # pc "Hey"
    pc "Olá"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:20
translate portuguese jamiephone1_e6b33c25:

    # gnd "Hey, [pcname]. How's it going?"
    gnd "Olá, [pcname]. Como estás?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:21
translate portuguese jamiephone1_d57f9715:

    # pc "Pretty good, what's up?"
    pc "Muito bem, o que se passa?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:22
translate portuguese jamiephone1_ab588a54:

    # gnd "Just felt like talking to you. You got some time?"
    gnd "Apenas me apeteceu falar contigo. Tens algum tempo?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:25
translate portuguese jamiephone1_cf8b9e59:

    # pc "Sure, I got time."
    pc "Claro, tenho tempo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:29
translate portuguese jamiephone1_c2cf9bb6:

    # gnd "Wow, natural charmer aren't ya?"
    gnd "Uau, és um sedutor nato, não és?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:30
translate portuguese jamiephone1_80cdcc09:

    # pc "I like talking to you."
    pc "Gosto de falar contigo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:31
translate portuguese jamiephone1_5d93fddb:

    # gnd "Good. I like talking to you too."
    gnd "Ótimo. Também gosto de falar contigo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:34
translate portuguese jamiephone1_ca582ae4:

    # gnd "Oh, that's too bad. I'll talk to you some other time then."
    gnd "Oh, que pena. Falaremos noutra altura, então."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:35
translate portuguese jamiephone1_66ec96d3:

    # gnd "Sorry to bother you. Talk to you later."
    gnd "Desculpa incomodar-te. Falamos mais tarde."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:36
translate portuguese jamiephone1_f01523d0:

    # "She hangs up the phone and I put it back into my pocket."
    "Ela desliga o telefone e eu volto a colocá-lo no bolso."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:42
translate portuguese jamiephone1_62e5dd7e:

    # pc "So what's going on?"
    pc "Então, o que se passa?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:44
translate portuguese jamiephone1_d8868bcd:

    # gnd "Just been a rough week at school."
    gnd "Tem sido uma semana difícil na escola."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:45
translate portuguese jamiephone1_d87c0f62:

    # pc "Really? You're usually so good at school. What are you struggling with?"
    pc "A sério? Normalmente és tão bom na escola. Com o que é que estás a ter dificuldades?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:46
translate portuguese jamiephone1_7e66235e:

    # gnd "I'm not really struggling with any of the schoolwork."
    gnd "Na verdade, não estou a ter dificuldades com nenhum dos trabalhos escolares."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:47
translate portuguese jamiephone1_43b9e385:

    # gnd "It's the in-class teaching program."
    gnd "É o programa de ensino em sala de aula."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:48
translate portuguese jamiephone1_d6457b46:

    # gnd "I have to stand in front of all of these students and teach."
    gnd "Tenho de ficar à frente de todos estes alunos e dar aula."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:49
translate portuguese jamiephone1_bc8e7906:

    # gnd "I'm just having a hard time standing at the front of the class with all of them looking at me."
    gnd "Estou apenas a ter dificuldade em ficar à frente da turma com todos a olharem para mim."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:50
translate portuguese jamiephone1_c80b503a:

    # pc "You're scared of public speaking?"
    pc "Tens medo de falar em público?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:51
translate portuguese jamiephone1_15bcf641:

    # gnd "I guess so. I've never really had to do a lot of it. It's just uncomfortable having all eyes on me. It makes me really self-conscious."
    gnd "Acho que sim. Nunca tive de o fazer muitas vezes. É apenas desconfortável ter todos os olhos postos em mim. Faz-me sentir muito constrangida."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:54
translate portuguese jamiephone1_1eff5d82:

    # gnd "I'm sure you're right, it's just hard right now."
    gnd "Tenho a certeza de que tens razão, mas neste momento é difícil."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:57
translate portuguese jamiephone1_b138a837:

    # gnd "What do you mean?"
    gnd "O que queres dizer?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:58
translate portuguese jamiephone1_ecd76308:

    # pc "Well you're beautiful. I'm sure that guys stare at you all the time."
    pc "Bem, tu és linda. Tenho a certeza de que os rapazes ficam a olhar para ti o tempo todo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:59
translate portuguese jamiephone1_c31f5d75:

    # gnd "You think I'm beautiful?"
    gnd "Achas que sou linda?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:60
translate portuguese jamiephone1_dd9bd446:

    # pc "Of course you are."
    pc "Claro que és."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:62
translate portuguese jamiephone1_a5543b0a:

    # gnd "Thanks, [pcname]."
    gnd "Obrigada, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:63
translate portuguese jamiephone1_92d2aff8:

    # gnd "But as nice as that is, it doesn't really help me with the public speaking."
    gnd "Mas, por mais simpático que isso seja, não me ajuda muito com o discurso em público."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:66
translate portuguese jamiephone1_9cc47622:

    # gnd "[pcname]!"
    gnd "[pcname]!"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:67
translate portuguese jamiephone1_58f48bda:

    # gnd "I've heard of that method before, but in this case the audience is a bunch of thirteen-year-olds."
    gnd "Já ouvi falar desse método antes, mas, neste caso, o público é um grupo de miúdos de 13 anos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:68
translate portuguese jamiephone1_84faa7b7:

    # pc "Oh right. Not a good idea then."
    pc "Ah, certo. Então não é uma boa ideia."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:70
translate portuguese jamiephone1_ba2f8001:

    # gnd "Right. Bad idea, try again."
    gnd "Exato. Má ideia, tenta outra vez."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:71
translate portuguese jamiephone1_c0af307c:

    # pc "Maybe you could practice your lessons ahead of time on me?"
    pc "Talvez pudesses praticar as tuas aulas comigo antes?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:73
translate portuguese jamiephone1_032af84e:

    # gnd "You'd do that for me?"
    gnd "Farias isso por mim?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:74
translate portuguese jamiephone1_2bf7afc7:

    # pc "Sure, just let me know and I'll listen to your lessons. Then during class, you can just pretend that you're giving your lessons to me again."
    pc "Claro, basta avisares-me e eu ouço as tuas aulas. Depois, durante a aula, podes simplesmente fingir que estás a dar-me as aulas outra vez."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:75
translate portuguese jamiephone1_73d793ae:

    # pc "After a while, the butterflies will probably go away."
    pc "Depois de algum tempo, o nervosismo provavelmente vai desaparecer."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:77
translate portuguese jamiephone1_cadb83e9:

    # gnd "That's actually a pretty good idea."
    gnd "Na verdade, é uma ideia muito boa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:78
translate portuguese jamiephone1_79c9211e:

    # pc "I have them occasionally."
    pc "Eu tenho isso de vez em quando."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:80
translate portuguese jamiephone1_8dab1990:

    # gnd "Thanks, [pcname]. I'll let you know when I need you to listen to a lesson."
    gnd "Obrigado, [pcname]. Eu aviso-te quando precisar que ouças uma aula."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:81
translate portuguese jamiephone1_050f909c:

    # pc "Sounds good."
    pc "Parece-me bem."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:82
translate portuguese jamiephone1_1bf27b6a:

    # gnd "Have you been doing okay in school?"
    gnd "Tens-te saído bem na escola?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:83
translate portuguese jamiephone1_f033e017:

    # pc "It's been going okay so far."
    pc "Tem corrido bem até agora."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:85
translate portuguese jamiephone1_5e1eb57b:

    # gnd "Well if you need someone to study with, you can come hang out with me pretty much any weekday night while my dad's at work."
    gnd "Bem, se precisares de alguém com quem estudar, podes vir passar tempo comigo praticamente em qualquer noite da semana, enquanto o meu pai está no trabalho."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:86
translate portuguese jamiephone1_b0435202:

    # pc "That sounds fun."
    pc "Isso parece divertido."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:87
translate portuguese jamiephone1_d41eb353:

    # gnd "I don't know about fun. It's studying. But I'd be glad to help you."
    gnd "Não sei se é divertido. É estudar. Mas terei todo o gosto em ajudar-te."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:88
translate portuguese jamiephone1_57376a44:

    # pc "Thanks, Jamie, I'll probably take you up on that."
    pc "Obrigada, Jamie, provavelmente vou aceitar a tua oferta."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:89
translate portuguese jamiephone1_6b6bc48a:

    # gnd "I hope so."
    gnd "Espero que sim."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:91
translate portuguese jamiephone1_1b403d26:

    # gnd "Alright, [pcname], thanks for listening. It's getting pretty late, I better go to bed."
    gnd "Muito bem, [pcname], obrigada por me ouvires. Está a ficar bastante tarde, é melhor ir para a cama."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:92
translate portuguese jamiephone1_fb7cffd0:

    # pc "Okay, good night."
    pc "Está bem, boa noite."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:93
translate portuguese jamiephone1_e206e304:

    # gnd "Night, [pcname]."
    gnd "Boa noite, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:95
translate portuguese jamiephone1_6865bc2c:

    # "She hangs up and I put the phone on my nightstand. She's right, it is getting pretty late. Better get ready for bed."
    "Ela desliga e eu coloco o telefone na minha mesinha de cabeceira. Ela tem razão, está a ficar bastante tarde. É melhor preparar-me para dormir."

